novartis bioventures ltd
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Asset Management
Sub-Industry: Private Equity
Novartis BioVentures Ltd operates as a venture capital firm. The Company invests in life sciences companies including biotechnology, biopharma, medical devices, and diagnostics. Novartis Venture Funds serves customers worldwide.




