description
Novartis Bioventure Fund primary focus is on the development of novel therapeutics and platforms. In their investments we look for unmet need and clinical impact, novel proprietary science and understanding of mechanism, management and board experience and capital efficiency in the program. They invest in North America, Europe, Israel and Asia/Pacific and manage over USD 1 billion in committed capital and more than 40 portfolio companies. They continue their strategy of making larger focused investments and anticipate total investments up to USD 30 million per company over its life.









